sets.detail:
200 Melee Attack with Brawny is to hit as hard as possible 
 200 Speed with Nimble and Boots outspeeds Boots Tahtab, without Boots, outspeeds Nimble Vesperatu 
 12 Energy = 250 Energy at level 50 for (2 Vicious Snaps + 1 Mega Chomp + 1 Barter + 2 Chilly Chomps) 
 64 Ranged Defense gives Protogon a Melee Attack Boost 
 24 HP is leftovers and increases bulk a little
